thread.title: Pakistan's central bank cuts benchmark interest rate to 6.5 percent
thread.title_full: Pakistan's central bank cuts benchmark interest rate to 6.5 percent | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Pakistan's central bank cuts benchmark interest rate to 6.5 percent
text:
KARACHI, July 25 Pakistan's central bank cut its benchmark interest rate by 50 basis points to 6.5 percent on Saturday, a spokesman said.
The bank has gradually reduced the interest rate as it seeks to spur economic growth against a backdrop of slowing inflation, largely due to weak oil prices. (Reporting by Syed Raza Hassan; Writing by Katharine Houreld ; Editing by Jeremy Laurence)
